WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:12.272
Because he's put some things about October that are very strategic concerning the glory, the outpouring, and praying into it.

00:00:12.272 --> 00:00:22.899
So, Pastor Paul Begley with his channel—I don't know if many of you are familiar with Pastor Paul Begley, but he goes, 'Are you serious?

00:00:22.899 --> 00:00:23.209
Are you serious?

00:00:23.209 --> 00:00:27.016
'—that guy called me.

00:00:27.016 --> 00:00:32.559
He emailed my wife and said, 'I want to talk to your husband.

