' I waited because the Lord told me to, as one of his team members had reached out in August.

00:00:52.990 --> 00:00:58.800
The Lord said, 'No, don't talk to him yet.

00:00:58.800 --> 00:01:10.939
' And he didn't know that the Lord had said that to me, because the Lord had also said to him, 'Don't talk to him yet.

00:01:10.939 --> 00:01:23.999
' I thought that was interesting because after we talked yesterday—we talked for over an hour on the phone—my goodness, I tell you what, I felt the Holy Ghost.

00:01:24.532 --> 00:01:31.955
And instantaneously, when I was talking to Pastor Paul Begley on the phone, I went into the spirit and started seeing things for his future.

00:01:39.669 --> 00:01:40.240
But I wasn't allowed to tell him what I was seeing because the Holy Spirit said to save that.

00:01:44.410 --> 00:01:44.680
He said, 'Don't say that.

00:01:54.856 --> 00:01:55.050
I want you to hold that.

00:01:55.050 --> 00:01:59.840
' So there were things that the Lord was showing me.

00:01:59.840 --> 00:02:03.497
But we're going to do some broadcasts together.

00:02:12.591 --> 00:02:12.943
He wants me to talk about some things, and he's going to use it for later on and have it on his channel for you all.

00:02:13.472 --> 00:02:14.900
So I'm going to talk and do some things for him.

00:02:16.190 --> 00:02:18.800
I don't do interviews very often unless the Holy Spirit tells me to.

00:02:18.992 --> 00:02:26.560
So, I'm going to do some interviews with Paul Begley in the next couple of days, and then he's going to broadcast them on his channel.

00:02:26.560 --> 00:02:31.268
He told me maybe ten days or so—I don't remember exactly.

00:02:48.133 --> 00:02:48.356
But he said he wanted to use them, so I told him I'd do it.

00:02:48.356 --> 00:02:54.480
Like I said, I don't usually do that, so it's only by the unction of the Holy Spirit.

00:02:56.258 --> 00:02:58.640
I'm going to go on Paul Begley's channel sometime this week and do some things for him.

00:02:58.640 --> 00:03:04.960
Then I'm going to go to Sister Billie Brim's prayer conference in Branson, Missouri.

00:03:08.399 --> 00:03:12.080
I don't know what I'll do there, but she asked me to come.

00:03:12.080 --> 00:03:14.093
She said, 'Would you come?

00:03:14.093 --> 00:03:16.759
' and I said, 'I will come.

00:03:16.759 --> 00:03:24.480
' I don't know what she has in mind, but I'm going to go by the spirit of the unction for what I feel inside.

00:03:25.440 --> 00:03:29.795
If I can make it to Tennessee for Billy Burke at the Harvest Church, I will.

00:03:29.795 --> 00:03:45.211
But if the Lord has me stay at Billie's for the tent revival—there is a tent revival on her property, and they always have a fish fry and all that stuff, and she's asked me to come—I'm still praying about that.

00:03:45.920 --> 00:03:53.737
I don't know if I'll go or not, but I'm just putting my feelers out there, asking the Holy Spirit, 'What do you want me to do?

00:03:53.737 --> 00:03:59.400
' I really feel drawn to Billy Burke and his services in Tennessee.

00:03:59.400 --> 00:04:06.070
More than likely, I might go that direction because I want to support him and I already told you I would.

00:04:06.070 --> 00:04:12.879
There are so many of you traveling, but I haven't made up my mind yet; I'm still praying.

00:04:23.280 --> 00:04:34.020
That is why I wanted to give you an update about everything, because people wanted to know, 'Where are you?

00:04:34.020 --> 00:04:34.700
What's going on?

00:04:34.700 --> 00:04:35.620
Are you okay?

00:04:35.620 --> 00:04:37.070
' Yes, I'm okay.

00:04:37.724 --> 00:04:41.830
I just push things away when they get in my space.

00:04:41.830 --> 00:04:46.309
You ain't taking over me and Jesus.

00:04:46.309 --> 00:04:49.771
With YouTube, I've got to keep things real.

00:04:49.771 --> 00:04:55.759
So, we're going to go over all of that.

00:04:55.759 --> 00:04:57.938
Have I been talking thirteen minutes?

00:04:57.938 --> 00:05:03.349
Oh, man, that's too much.

00:05:05.703 --> 00:05:07.806
It's live; if this wasn't live, he would have cut it.

00:05:07.806 --> 00:05:11.062
You wouldn't have heard any of that, hardly.

00:05:14.595 --> 00:05:14.897
I usually keep it to five minutes.

00:05:14.897 --> 00:05:18.710
He might still cut it, I don't know.

00:05:38.224 --> 00:05:38.472
But let's go over the Tomahawk missiles and what the Lord showed us concerning World War III and what I believe is coming.

00:05:38.472 --> 00:05:42.009
The more I prayed into it, the more the Lord showed me.

00:05:42.009 --> 00:05:49.960
Sorry my voice is raspy, but I'm not coughing as much because I've got some good stuff and it's really helping me.

00:05:50.590 --> 00:05:51.136
I'm feeling a lot better.

00:05:57.547 --> 00:05:57.929
My voice still sounds groggy, but it's nothing like it was.

00:06:16.160 --> 00:06:16.530
And I'm drinking my soda, and this stuff is good.

00:06:22.240 --> 00:06:22.760
I told Braden I've enjoyed this cream soda by Zevia.

00:06:22.760 --> 00:06:23.700
What?

00:06:23.700 --> 00:06:26.639
Fifty percent are not from America?

00:06:26.639 --> 00:06:30.857
Get out of here!

00:06:30.857 --> 00:06:31.680
Fifty percent!

00:06:31.680 --> 00:06:33.640
Well, welcome.

00:06:33.640 --> 00:06:36.631
That's awesome; I'm glad you're here.

00:06:36.631 --> 00:06:56.766
This is not usually how I do it, but I wanted to come on and just talk to you all and say hi, say some stuff real quick, and get off here because people are freaking out, asking, 'Where is he?

00:06:56.766 --> 00:07:01.154
' I just had to take some time.

00:07:03.120 --> 00:07:09.600
I don't put my lips to that because it's dirty; I have to wipe it off.

00:07:09.600 --> 00:07:12.142
But okay, let's be real.

00:07:12.142 --> 00:07:16.470
I saw by the Spirit of God an escalation of things.

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:40.000
And the Lord told me yesterday in my prayer time, 'I warned you that a great shaking to awaken is coming.

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:56.355
' And when I went into the spirit yesterday driving and praying, looking ahead to the rest of the fall and going into December, He said, 'There is a shaking to awaken.

00:08:19.580 --> 00:08:20.090
It's coming, Brandon.

00:08:27.440 --> 00:08:30.679
It's here.

00:08:30.679 --> 00:08:40.880
' And I warned you to watch Israel after the 23rd of September, that a great escalation of things would start to take place concerning the fig tree.

00:08:46.560 --> 00:08:47.359
And that's where we are.

00:08:47.359 --> 00:08:51.352
That's where we are.

00:08:52.959 --> 00:08:57.706
I believe we're at a great escalation of things like we've never seen before.

00:08:57.706 --> 00:09:07.680
We're at a time on earth right now where we are seeing the fig tree blossom.

00:09:20.039 --> 00:09:23.112
The coming of the Lord Jesus Christ is right at hand, and I'm telling you all, we're about to see the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen.

00:09:23.903 --> 00:09:28.731
And the Lord told me, 'Brandon, the shaking is coming to awaken the people.

00:09:43.519 --> 00:09:44.111
Remember what I told you, they're coming in hot.

00:09:44.111 --> 00:09:46.800
They're coming in hot.

00:09:46.800 --> 00:09:51.991
' So, He wanted me to go to a church service.

00:09:54.800 --> 00:09:55.240
I'm just going to be real with you all.

00:10:08.213 --> 00:10:08.426
And He said, 'Wear pink shorts.

00:10:08.426 --> 00:10:13.600
' He said, 'I want you to sit on the front row.

00:10:13.600 --> 00:10:19.833
' And I said, 'What?

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:26.910
You want me to go and wear pink shorts and sit on the front row?

00:10:26.910 --> 00:10:30.794
' He said, 'Yeah, it's for you and for them.

00:10:30.794 --> 00:10:35.839
' So, I got my pink shorts on.

00:10:35.839 --> 00:10:38.504
I'd show them to you if I could.

00:10:38.504 --> 00:10:41.120
It's kind of embarrassing, but I wore these pink shorts.

00:10:41.120 --> 00:10:43.298
Here, I'll show you.

00:10:43.298 --> 00:10:45.620
Can you see them?

00:10:45.620 --> 00:10:52.423
Yeah, these are bright pink shorts.

00:10:53.216 --> 00:10:57.040
And I wore these because of the unction of the Holy Spirit.

00:10:57.573 --> 00:11:12.020
The Lord said, 'Brandon, I want you to put on pink shorts and go and sit on the front row.

00:11:12.020 --> 00:11:14.110
' I said, 'Good Lord!

00:11:28.720 --> 00:11:28.933
Lord, you want me to do that?

00:11:28.933 --> 00:11:32.639
' Oh, it's my green screen now.

00:11:32.639 --> 00:11:40.575
You can't see that; I don't sit behind flowers.

00:11:44.916 --> 00:11:45.244
Is it working?

00:11:45.244 --> 00:11:45.902
Yeah.

00:11:45.902 --> 00:11:49.982
So, I went and I put on my pink shorts.

00:11:49.982 --> 00:11:54.036
Diana said, 'Are you wearing that to church?

00:11:54.036 --> 00:11:55.680
' I said, 'Yes.

00:11:55.680 --> 00:12:05.160
The Lord said to wear pink shorts, put them on, and go sit on the front row.

00:12:05.160 --> 00:12:11.990
' She goes, 'It's a night service.

00:12:12.000 --> 00:12:13.822
' I said, 'Yeah.

00:12:14.915 --> 00:12:18.747
I don't know why, but it's to humble me, I guess.

00:12:18.747 --> 00:12:23.040
' But I obeyed.

00:12:49.147 --> 00:12:49.560
And when I sat in there, with all the people dressed up, they were looking at me and I was looking at them.

00:13:02.480 --> 00:13:02.738
And He said, 'Remember, the babies are coming.

00:13:02.738 --> 00:13:04.542
How will you handle the babies?

00:13:04.542 --> 00:13:06.400
Be patient with My babies.

00:13:06.400 --> 00:13:11.493
Brandon, I tell you to do things more to check their hearts than to check yours.

00:13:11.493 --> 00:13:12.836
This isn't about you.

00:13:12.836 --> 00:13:33.760
' 'What does it have to do with me wearing pink shorts to a night service, and here I am, the guy with the big YouTube channel?

00:13:33.760 --> 00:13:41.680
' 'Just do what I asked you to do.

00:13:43.828 --> 00:13:44.262
I'm doing something.

00:13:44.262 --> 00:13:46.304
' But I obeyed.

00:13:46.304 --> 00:13:58.560
Do you know, when William Seymour said, 'Put the box on your head,' the Lord said, 'Put the box on your head and sit in the corner'?

00:13:58.560 --> 00:14:02.674
That sounds crazy, but put the box on.

00:14:02.674 --> 00:14:07.451
If He says to do it, do it.

00:14:07.451 --> 00:14:15.189
Whatever He says to do, do it, no matter if you look foolish or not.

00:14:23.360 --> 00:14:23.872
And in this case, I felt foolish, but I said, "Lord, I'll do it.

00:14:23.872 --> 00:14:31.564
" So, I put the pink shorts on and I sat on the front row.

00:14:53.660 --> 00:14:54.050
I usually sit in the back, but the pastor saved me a front row seat and I had shorts on with no socks.

00:14:54.050 --> 00:15:01.999
So I sat in there and the Lord told me, he said, "Brandon, there's something more to this.

00:15:01.999 --> 00:15:04.099
" So I felt the Holy Ghost.

00:15:04.099 --> 00:15:10.039
I prayed in the spirit the whole time and I could see people watching.

00:15:10.039 --> 00:15:15.737
I knew they were glaring and they're looking, but the Lord said, "I'm doing something.

00:15:15.737 --> 00:15:19.220
There's something more to this, but I just obey.

00:15:21.840 --> 00:15:35.560
" So, all that to say this, he showed me a lot of my church is not ready for what's about to take place.

00:15:48.160 --> 00:15:50.960
I cannot go into the depth of what he said, but he gave me a word and he said, "Brandon, I'm going to show you something.

00:15:50.960 --> 00:16:00.129
" And he said, "A lot of my church is not ready for what's about to take place in this earth.

00:16:01.980 --> 00:16:05.964
" He said, "You see it, don't you?

00:16:19.219 --> 00:16:21.270
What I wanted you to see?

00:16:38.671 --> 00:16:38.880
" He downloaded things.

00:16:39.296 --> 00:16:39.920
I said, "Yes, sir.

00:16:52.320 --> 00:16:52.526
" He said, "A great shaking is going to awaken a lot of the church.

00:16:52.526 --> 00:16:59.646
" Now, is that concerning everybody in that church that I went to?

00:16:59.646 --> 00:17:00.667
No.

00:17:00.667 --> 00:17:05.027
He's examining the hearts of the troops through people and foolishness.

00:17:05.027 --> 00:17:07.493
Put a box on your head.

00:17:07.493 --> 00:17:09.093
William Seymour put it on.

00:17:09.093 --> 00:17:14.746
He goes, "I don't know why, but there's something about the box.

00:17:14.746 --> 00:17:22.740
" And the moment he put the box on, he could have it on for 45 minutes.

00:17:22.740 --> 00:17:28.034
He could have it on for two hours.

00:17:28.034 --> 00:17:30.949
He could have it on for 10 minutes.

00:17:30.949 --> 00:17:39.600
But in his moment the Lord said to take the box off, the glory came in Azusa.

00:17:39.600 --> 00:17:45.413
So I'm learning he does things like that to me and it's a test.

00:17:45.413 --> 00:17:50.080
Will you do what I ask you to?

00:17:50.080 --> 00:17:56.880
So he told me, he said, "I'm examining my troops and a lot of them are not ready.

00:17:56.880 --> 00:18:02.240
A lot of people are not ready, Brandon, for what's coming.

00:18:02.240 --> 00:18:05.540
" But they will be.

00:18:05.540 --> 00:18:08.480
I want you to hear me.

00:18:08.480 --> 00:18:15.679
He said, "I'm going to shake my church, Brandon, and there will be shaking more than what happened with Charlie.

00:18:15.679 --> 00:18:33.920
There's going to be a great awakening come and there will be a great outpouring of my spirit upon this earth like they've never seen before.

00:18:33.920 --> 00:18:39.964
For I'm giving them one last call and the boat is shutting.

00:18:50.000 --> 00:18:50.309
The door of the ark is going to close abruptly.

00:18:50.309 --> 00:19:06.680
No man knows the day or the hour, but I'm telling you, ladies and gentlemen, that the spirit of the Lord told me yesterday in my prayer time—well, not even yesterday, was it less than six hours ago?

00:19:18.080 --> 00:19:18.400
He said, 'I'm coming, Brandon.

00:19:18.400 --> 00:19:19.359
I'm coming.

00:19:19.359 --> 00:19:22.620
I warned you.

00:19:22.620 --> 00:19:30.200
I was standing at the door, Brandon, and many in my church is not awake.

00:19:30.200 --> 00:19:34.947
There's some of them that are awake.

00:19:34.947 --> 00:19:36.731
Some of them.

00:19:36.731 --> 00:19:44.903
' But he said, 'For what's about to take place in this earth, they will all be awake.

00:19:44.903 --> 00:19:48.850
Even the heathen, even the world is about to be awake.

00:19:55.536 --> 00:19:55.744
They're going to be awake.

00:19:55.744 --> 00:19:58.860
' What you want to say, they're awake.

00:20:03.017 --> 00:20:03.429
And a great—there will be so much shaking take place.

00:20:03.429 --> 00:20:04.800
Five major shakings.

00:20:04.800 --> 00:20:05.440
Five.

00:20:06.080 --> 00:20:11.540
And all of them will shake like labor pains upon a woman.

00:20:16.900 --> 00:20:21.280
He said to me, he said, 'What you're about to experience is seed time and harvest at its fullest.

00:20:21.280 --> 00:20:29.691
I have delayed the harvest of many souls, of what you have.

00:20:29.691 --> 00:20:34.809
' He said, 'My word does not return unto me void.

00:20:34.809 --> 00:20:39.440
Whatsoever a man sows, that will he also reap.

00:20:39.440 --> 00:20:45.960
You sow to the flesh, you reap of the flesh.

00:21:13.440 --> 00:21:14.636
You sow to the spirit, you reap of the spirit.

00:21:14.636 --> 00:21:23.406
' And he said, 'Many people, Brandon, have sowed and sowed, and the world has never reaped.

00:21:32.519 --> 00:21:34.619
And what you're about to see is a full manifestation of reaping that you've never seen before, called the Great Tribulation.

00:21:37.097 --> 00:21:41.680
But right now, the church is going through a great awakening.

00:21:41.680 --> 00:21:47.139
' And what he showed me, I saw it all in a vision.

00:21:47.139 --> 00:21:54.517
Seed time and harvest, right now where we are, as labor pains upon a woman, the beginning of sorrows.

00:21:54.517 --> 00:22:04.272
He said, 'That's where you are, that's right.

00:22:04.272 --> 00:22:21.672
' The dispensation of grace is about to come to an end and he said, 'You're coming to the door of the Great Tribulation.

00:22:25.200 --> 00:22:26.720
The catching away of the church is right ahead.

00:22:26.720 --> 00:22:32.880
' But a major move of God, my presence is grace, one more grace explosion right now with the church.

00:22:45.330 --> 00:22:45.640
You think what we're about to see is judgment, but it's God's grace waking you up as a good dad correcting his church.

00:22:45.640 --> 00:22:54.149
It's a good dad correcting the people, saying, 'Hey, I'm giving you one more chance.

00:22:54.149 --> 00:23:04.497
' So you experience some hardships, you experiencing some earthquakes, you experiencing things with the great birthing pains, the labor pains, all these things.

00:23:04.853 --> 00:23:07.130
You think, 'Well, that's tribulation.

00:23:07.130 --> 00:23:14.738
' No, you've never experienced what they're about to experience.

00:23:16.381 --> 00:23:18.760
You don't want to experience what's about to happen.

00:23:18.760 --> 00:23:26.672
No man has ever experienced what's about to happen.

00:23:34.177 --> 00:23:35.635
You think the disciples went through something?

00:23:48.1000 --> 00:23:49.520
You think the plagues of the past were something?

00:24:05.459 --> 00:24:05.760
You have no clue of what's about to take place because the Bible says no man has ever seen what's about to take place.

00:24:15.279 --> 00:24:15.908
You think some hurricanes that were bad?

00:24:15.908 --> 00:24:20.125
Maybe some disease on some animals.

00:24:20.125 --> 00:24:23.695
Folks, tribulation will be hell on earth.

00:24:23.695 --> 00:24:26.860
And that's what I'm trying to tell you all.

00:24:33.536 --> 00:24:35.420
The Lord said to me in my prayer time, he said, 'Brandon, I'm going to give an explosion of grace.

00:24:44.000 --> 00:24:47.360
The great healing revivals of the past will hold nothing compared to what's about to take place.

00:24:47.360 --> 00:24:50.391
Salvations like you've never seen it.

00:24:50.391 --> 00:24:54.720
You're at the door of it, but my church isn't ready for it.

00:24:54.720 --> 00:24:56.080
They're still asleep.

00:24:56.080 --> 00:24:59.680
So, judgment begins in the house of the Lord first.

00:24:59.680 --> 00:25:01.111
He's shaking the church first.

00:25:18.532 --> 00:25:18.799
And you're about to see a shaking inside of the church, from the Catholics to the Baptists.

00:25:19.391 --> 00:25:25.190
It's not about the Charismatics.

00:25:25.200 --> 00:25:28.848
It's not about the Church of God.

00:25:28.848 --> 00:25:34.768
It's not about the Assemblies of God.

00:25:51.720 --> 00:25:52.180
This is about all hands on deck.

00:25:52.180 --> 00:25:58.159
Catholic, Baptist, Methodist, it don't matter what tent you're in.

00:25:58.159 --> 00:26:08.208
It's about getting the lost saved and bringing them into the saving knowledge of Jesus Christ before it's too late.

00:26:17.813 --> 00:26:18.360
The ark door's closing and it's time to put our petty differences down of what we've been always taught.

00:26:18.360 --> 00:26:23.337
'Well, you know, they're Baptist, they're Methodist, they're Catholic.

00:26:23.337 --> 00:26:33.920
' No, we're the body of Christ moving as one, bringing in the lost and bringing them to his Son.

00:26:33.920 --> 00:26:35.540
Do you understand?

00:26:44.587 --> 00:26:44.782
And saying, 'Hey, you need to get saved because you're running out of time.

00:26:44.782 --> 00:26:45.564
Jesus is coming.

00:26:45.564 --> 00:26:46.450
Jesus is coming.

00:26:46.450 --> 00:26:51.733
' He said it in my tongues, I could hear him.

00:26:58.871 --> 00:26:59.236
And he said to me, 'Brandon, I'm coming.

00:26:59.236 --> 00:27:05.280
' Do you understand?

00:27:05.280 --> 00:27:09.051
Do you really understand that Jesus is coming?

00:27:09.051 --> 00:27:12.387
'Oh, I've heard that before, brother.

00:27:12.387 --> 00:27:26.000
' But I'm here to tell you again tonight, today, this morning, early early morning here in America, that Jesus Christ is coming.

00:27:36.514 --> 00:27:36.766
And you're about to see a great shaking to awaken.

00:27:51.880 --> 00:27:52.080
God have mercy on those that do not wake up this time.

00:27:52.080 --> 00:27:54.399
For this is an act of grace.

00:27:54.399 --> 00:27:58.096
Leaving the 99 to go after the one.

00:27:58.096 --> 00:28:02.800
Leaving the 99 to go after the one.

00:28:08.499 --> 00:28:09.279
Are you the one?

00:28:20.125 --> 00:28:28.891
For God so loved the world that he gave his one and only Son, that whosoever will believe in him should not perish but have everlasting life.

00:28:28.891 --> 00:28:49.680
