Separate yourself and look at Him.

01:00:54.549 --> 01:01:01.800
It's like my friend says: to detract, to deflect, to attract—to deflect to the glory, to Jesus.

01:01:01.800 --> 01:01:08.040
He said to me, He said, "Brandon, because I'm like a spiritual junkie.

01:01:14.000 --> 01:01:16.423
I go from these places and I try to pull from the minister a lot and go, 'Oh, God, give me a touch from Jesus in here.

01:01:25.720 --> 01:01:25.920
I want it so bad.

01:01:25.920 --> 01:01:28.080
' He said, 'Brandon, where do you think they got it?

01:01:28.080 --> 01:01:30.586
Straight from me.

01:01:30.586 --> 01:01:37.680
' He said, 'There's a place where you always keep yourself full.

01:01:40.1000 --> 01:01:41.300
You don't need nobody.

01:01:41.300 --> 01:01:49.280
' I said, 'Yeah, I know, Lord, but I like to go and just get—it's like a spiritual high.

01:01:49.280 --> 01:01:50.380
' Do you understand?

01:01:50.380 --> 01:02:00.720
It's like, 'I love it for my kids to experience it and see the atmosphere.

01:02:00.720 --> 01:02:07.680
' He said, 'Learn to cultivate it yourself on a greater level.

01:02:07.680 --> 01:02:12.789
Learn to get in there even greater with me.

01:02:12.789 --> 01:02:19.706
' And that's what I did this week, and I found it more.

01:02:23.668 --> 01:02:23.965
And then, stay in your vein.

01:02:26.040 --> 01:02:27.840
Don't try to deviate and be in somebody else's call.

01:02:27.840 --> 01:02:34.916
Stay in what God has called and anointed and graced you to do.

01:02:34.916 --> 01:02:38.860
Not all people are going to be a special healing evangelist.

01:02:38.860 --> 01:02:42.808
Not all people are going to see and do things like God has called me to do.

01:02:42.808 --> 01:02:45.879
But what has God graced you to do?

01:02:45.879 --> 01:02:47.180
Stay in your vein.

01:02:47.180 --> 01:02:56.640
Don't go and try to be like sister so-and-so or brother so-and-so.

01:03:01.368 --> 01:03:03.929
Be what God has called you to do.

01:03:19.236 --> 01:03:19.835
And whatever He calls you to do, do all that you do in word and in deed.

01:03:19.835 --> 01:03:23.981
Do all to the glory of God.

01:03:41.269 --> 01:03:41.459
He showed me there's levels of glory.

01:03:41.649 --> 01:03:43.074
There's levels of the anointing.

01:03:45.509 --> 01:03:45.760
There's levels of impartation.

01:03:48.447 --> 01:03:50.937
There's levels of My presence.

01:03:50.937 --> 01:04:07.479
There's a deep river that shall not run dry.

01:04:07.479 --> 01:04:10.360
There is a fountain that flows deep inside.

01:04:10.360 --> 01:04:11.039
Do you understand?

01:04:11.039 --> 01:04:13.623
Come to the river that never shall run dry.

01:04:13.623 --> 01:04:16.459
There is a vast supply.

01:04:16.459 --> 01:04:22.177
" And that's why he said, "Take the time every day, Father, fill me.

01:04:22.177 --> 01:04:30.640
" But he showed me the level of filling, the level of infilling is to your surrender.

01:04:30.640 --> 01:04:35.910
How much have you surrendered?

01:04:35.920 --> 01:04:43.828
How much have you gone through the refining?

01:04:43.828 --> 01:04:52.829
How much have you gone on the potter's wheel and allowed him to mold you and make you?

01:05:05.359 --> 01:05:05.679
He said the level of surrender is the level of filling.

01:05:05.679 --> 01:05:07.280
"Fill my cup, Lord.

01:05:07.280 --> 01:05:11.219
I lift it up, Lord.

01:05:11.219 --> 01:05:15.839
" But how much have you reserved of yourself for yourself?

01:05:15.839 --> 01:05:18.059
Let me say that again.

01:05:37.200 --> 01:05:37.707
How much have you reserved yourself for yourself?

01:05:37.707 --> 01:05:45.639
"Fill my cup, Lord," but I only give you so much space to fill up.

01:05:54.180 --> 01:05:54.390
"I lift it up, Lord," but you only have two inches.

01:05:54.390 --> 01:06:00.914
"Come and quench this thirsting of my soul.

01:06:00.914 --> 01:06:04.230
Bread of heaven, feed me till I want no more.

01:06:17.520 --> 01:06:17.960
" I only need two inches.

01:06:17.960 --> 01:06:21.700
There is a vast supply, but I only need two inches.

01:06:21.700 --> 01:06:23.040
One inch.

01:06:23.040 --> 01:06:27.543
Oh, some people are only a couple of centimeters.

01:06:32.194 --> 01:06:32.731
"I'm filled.

01:06:32.731 --> 01:06:34.343
I'm filled.

01:06:34.343 --> 01:06:42.133
" But he's like, "But I want to take you over.

01:06:47.200 --> 01:06:48.610
I want to fill you to the extreme until it overflows.

01:06:54.299 --> 01:06:54.759
" But there's a level of surrender.

01:06:54.759 --> 01:06:57.890
That's what he said to me.

01:07:09.240 --> 01:07:09.600
I said, "God, help me to be more surrendered.

01:07:09.600 --> 01:07:12.480
Help me to die more to myself.

01:07:19.200 --> 01:07:19.502
" There's a place in God the devil dare not go.

01:07:19.502 --> 01:07:26.008
But I realized as this week I took the time, I thought, how much of the refining process?

01:07:26.008 --> 01:07:31.793
Because he was showing me that the level of the glory depends upon the level of refining.

01:07:36.560 --> 01:07:36.880
The refining equals the level of the glory.

01:07:36.880 --> 01:07:39.566
Because I go, where's it at?

01:08:05.532 --> 01:08:07.063
Where do I die more?

01:08:13.690 --> 01:08:15.160
The Apostle Paul said, "I die daily.

01:08:15.160 --> 01:08:17.410
" What does that mean?

01:08:17.410 --> 01:08:25.787
And that's where I was at—that's where I've been, sitting at his feet.

01:08:25.787 --> 01:08:27.600
Where is that?

01:08:27.600 --> 01:08:29.360
Does he have all of me?

01:08:29.360 --> 01:08:33.700
Have I surrendered all to him?

01:08:33.700 --> 01:08:35.730
"I surrender all.

01:08:35.730 --> 01:08:40.319
" It's a beautiful song, but there's more to it.

01:09:03.040 --> 01:09:03.380
"I surrender all.

01:09:03.380 --> 01:09:06.911
All to thee, my blessed Savior, I surrender all.

01:09:06.911 --> 01:09:08.849
" Have I totally surrendered?

01:09:25.080 --> 01:09:25.920
Have I totally surrendered?

01:09:25.920 --> 01:09:30.120
"Fill my cup, Lord, I lift it up, Lord.

01:09:30.120 --> 01:09:35.552
Come and quench this thirsting of my soul.

01:09:35.552 --> 01:09:39.062
" It's at the place of surrender.

01:09:43.839 --> 01:09:54.669
I want so badly that none of me remains and only he is able to move in and through me, unhindered by any satanic or demonic spirit, uninterrupted and unhindered.

01:10:03.154 --> 01:10:05.714
"Father, here am I, use me, flow through me unhindered today without any Brandon in the way, flesh worried about what I say," because I say some stupid stuff.

01:10:21.960 --> 01:10:22.400
Thank God for his grace, thank God for his mercy.

01:10:22.400 --> 01:10:28.343
But it's at the level of the point of your surrender.

01:10:28.343 --> 01:10:31.920
That's what he said to me.

01:10:31.920 --> 01:10:33.933
Do you see this?

01:10:33.933 --> 01:10:36.000
You see that measure?

01:10:36.000 --> 01:10:40.800
Who I admire, it's the surrender.

01:10:55.692 --> 01:10:56.186
"I want to take you to the deeper waters.

01:11:11.244 --> 01:11:11.627
" And your mouth says a lot.

01:11:11.627 --> 01:11:13.538
That's what he said.

01:11:16.914 --> 01:11:17.291
"Your mouth says a lot.

01:11:17.291 --> 01:11:21.080
There's a lot of heart service.

01:11:21.080 --> 01:11:24.782
There's a lot of mouth service.

01:11:33.190 --> 01:11:33.520
" I say, "Oh, Lord, Lord, Lord," but he said, "But it's at the refining fire.

01:11:33.520 --> 01:11:46.559
It's at the level of death to yourself, to die to self, to the level of surrender, to be yielded to him, to flow with him.

01:12:00.500 --> 01:12:00.790
" And I saw, as I went down and got prayed for, the power of God knocked me down.

01:12:00.790 --> 01:12:01.949
Power knocked down.

01:12:15.234 --> 01:12:15.509
I had it what, three times, two times?

01:12:15.509 --> 01:12:16.331
Twice tonight.

01:12:32.811 --> 01:12:33.063
I sat there, I just drank.

01:12:33.063 --> 01:12:47.324
But what he said to me, he said, "Do you know whenever you hit a bend, you hit something and you've got baggage, and the more you hit something, it gets weaker and weaker?

01:12:59.337 --> 01:12:59.714
" And that's what the Holy Ghost does to that place in you that needs to die.

01:12:59.714 --> 01:13:01.223
It becomes weaker.

01:13:05.310 --> 01:13:09.782
And the more you allow him to put that pressure on you, it becomes weaker and weaker and weaker.

01:13:18.239 --> 01:13:28.030
And it's a washing, but it hits you like a wave, and eventually that levee will break in you.

01:13:36.434 --> 01:13:40.461
And he showed me, because I said, "Lord, I've been up there how many times over all the course of this, that I've needed a certain issue in me to be tested and refined.

01:13:40.461 --> 01:13:45.227
" And it was concerning something that happened clear back in 2015.

01:13:59.733 --> 01:14:00.226
And I've asked, I've laid down at the front how many times?

01:14:00.226 --> 01:14:03.120
Boom, power of God.

01:14:03.120 --> 01:14:03.600
Power of God.

01:14:03.600 --> 01:14:07.637
But there's levels of saturation.

01:14:07.637 --> 01:14:11.130
There's levels of the anointing, there's levels of saturation.

01:14:12.679 --> 01:14:14.773
And I realize the more I come underneath that presence, it keeps washing.

01:14:14.773 --> 01:14:16.106
It's like a wave.

01:14:18.400 --> 01:14:24.906
You know, if you sit on the shore of the ocean and the wave hits you, eventually it breaks.

01:14:32.453 --> 01:14:32.867
You know what I'm saying?

01:14:32.867 --> 01:14:34.879
That's what it feels like.

01:14:34.879 --> 01:14:49.400
And finally, all the times a stronghold, strongholds in your life, things that God is working and refining you, and it may be something you have a stronghold in and you think, "This is never coming off of me," but it just washes you.

01:14:51.537 --> 01:14:51.946
It wasn't the first time; it's levels of saturation.

01:14:51.946 --> 01:14:56.595
It's levels of saturation now.

01:15:02.751 --> 01:15:26.1000
You stand up, and I heard Sister Lynne Hammond talk about there's this one time that she was dealing with some depression in her life and she was dealing with this heaviness, and she went—and this special minister was there at her church—and he prayed for her, and the power of God knocked her down.

01:15:26.1000 --> 01:15:41.550
And she told the ushers, "You grab my arms and you pull me up even if I can't stand, and you drag me to the other side of the line and have him pray for me again.

01:15:54.434 --> 01:15:54.789
And you do this until I tell you to stop.

01:15:54.789 --> 01:16:00.519
" So she got prayed for.

01:16:00.519 --> 01:16:15.373
It was one of those lines that went through all the church, and she got up and she went to the back of the line.

01:16:15.373 --> 01:16:18.360
It's the level of saturation.

01:16:18.360 --> 01:16:39.653
She went five times, if I remember correctly, five times to the point that the Holy Spirit, that wave was hitting her so much until her cup, where she was in her dry time of what she was going through, that saturation came over her until it was broken, until her Holy Ghost level was completely filled up.

01:16:56.670 --> 01:16:56.880
They kept dragging her through the line, and it kept—the saturation, saturation.

01:16:56.880 --> 01:16:58.213
And that's what I experienced.

01:16:58.213 --> 01:17:00.180
That's what I'm trying to tell y'all.

01:17:00.180 --> 01:17:01.260
And it broke.

01:17:02.760 --> 01:17:03.060
"What was it, Brandon?

01:17:03.060 --> 01:17:04.560
" None of your business.

01:17:04.560 --> 01:17:06.649
Stuff that I work through with me.

01:17:06.649 --> 01:17:10.400
But I give all the glory to Jesus, do you understand?

01:17:25.906 --> 01:17:26.595
For he's changing me from earthly things to the heavenlies, his likeness and image to perfect in me, the love of God shown to the world.

01:17:26.595 --> 01:17:30.440
"Was it some secret sin, Brandon?

01:17:30.440 --> 01:17:31.159
" No.

01:17:31.159 --> 01:17:33.840
It has nothing to do with sin.

01:17:33.840 --> 01:17:36.880
It has nothing to do with temptation of sin.

01:17:36.880 --> 01:17:40.903
It has something to do with a character issue in me.

01:17:40.903 --> 01:17:46.782
It's me, because I want to be more like him.

01:17:46.782 --> 01:17:51.260
Being afraid of man, worried about people's opinion all the time.

01:17:51.260 --> 01:17:52.667
"Put on pink shorts.

01:17:52.667 --> 01:17:54.320
Brandon, remember my pink shorts?

01:17:54.320 --> 01:17:56.011
" He said, "Go.

01:17:56.011 --> 01:17:58.613
" So, can you see my pink shorts?

01:17:58.613 --> 01:18:03.320
"Go sit on the front row with pink shorts on, Brandon.

01:18:03.320 --> 01:18:06.159
" Oh my gosh.

01:18:06.159 --> 01:18:07.109
Are you kidding me?

01:18:11.040 --> 01:18:17.720
You want me to go wear pink shorts in the middle of church, in the middle of a revival night on the front row?

01:18:17.720 --> 01:18:28.229
"Go sit on the front row, but I want you to do it for me in the middle of...

01:18:28.229 --> 01:18:29.547
" "Yes, sir.

01:18:29.547 --> 01:18:33.410
" "William Seymour, put the box on your head.

01:18:33.410 --> 01:18:35.897
Do what I tell you to do.

01:18:35.897 --> 01:18:39.627
I'm doing something in you.

01:18:39.627 --> 01:18:42.591
But not only is it for you, it's for them.

01:18:42.591 --> 01:18:43.949
Somebody else out here.

01:18:43.949 --> 01:18:45.300
Somebody else out here.

01:18:54.293 --> 01:18:54.507
" What is it about?

01:19:04.987 --> 01:19:05.253
It doesn't matter.

01:19:05.253 --> 01:19:06.834
It's none of your business.

01:19:06.834 --> 01:19:13.817
"But I don't need to tell you what I'm doing in them just as much as I'm trying to do something in you.

01:19:13.817 --> 01:19:18.960
Just obey me and know that I'm working in somebody over here.

01:19:20.267 --> 01:19:26.319
And you don't even realize it.

01:19:26.319 --> 01:19:29.980
It's not always about you.

01:19:29.980 --> 01:19:31.360
" So, there's levels of saturation.

01:19:31.360 --> 01:19:42.206
I don't know where I'm going with all this at an hour and five minutes, but I felt like the Holy Spirit wanted me to tell you what Brandon's going through this week.

01:19:49.560 --> 01:19:49.810
You want to know what I'm dealing with?

01:19:49.810 --> 01:19:51.610
That's what I'm dealing with.

01:19:51.610 --> 01:19:53.977
And that's what he's dealing with.

01:19:53.977 --> 01:20:03.440
He's changing me from earthly things to the heavenlies, his likeness and image to perfect in me, the love of God shown to the world.

01:20:03.440 --> 01:20:06.560
From glory to glory, He's changing me.

01:20:06.560 --> 01:20:08.000
Changing me.

01:20:08.000 --> 01:20:09.691
Changing me.

01:20:09.691 --> 01:20:14.052
His likeness and image to perfect in me.

01:20:15.800 --> 01:20:17.640
The love of God shone to the world.

01:20:34.107 --> 01:20:34.373
For He's changing.

01:20:50.053 --> 01:20:50.640
He's changing me from earthly things to the heavenlies.

01:20:50.640 --> 01:20:51.813
There's levels of it.

01:20:59.590 --> 01:21:00.000
And that's why I said to Him, I don't know, I can't let my flowers fall down.

01:21:00.000 --> 01:21:03.698
Y'all think I forget I'm sitting on a brown couch.

01:21:03.698 --> 01:21:06.540
I'd stand up, mess up my pink shorts.

01:21:06.540 --> 01:21:13.030
But I'm just trying to tell you all we're all a work in progress.

01:21:19.440 --> 01:21:20.080
And you may be farther along than me in some areas, and I may be farther along than you in some areas.

01:21:20.080 --> 01:21:22.360
That's why we're the body of Christ and we work together.

01:21:22.360 --> 01:21:24.760
Not one of us is perfect.

01:21:24.760 --> 01:21:27.339
Not one of us is lesser in something.

01:21:27.339 --> 01:21:29.069
You say, "Well, Brandon, I don't deal with that.

01:21:29.069 --> 01:21:31.170
I don't deal with this.

01:21:38.320 --> 01:21:38.498
" But you deal with something else that I don't.

01:21:38.498 --> 01:21:39.209
Do you understand?

01:21:39.209 --> 01:21:45.289
But that's why I never try to shine a mirror on somebody's weakness and go, "Look at you.

01:21:49.703 --> 01:21:52.549
" I just say, "Hey, God, that's, you know," and I don't pick at it.

01:21:52.549 --> 01:21:55.780
Just go on about your business.

01:21:55.780 --> 01:21:58.719
We're all a work in progress.

01:21:58.719 --> 01:22:00.786
Does that make sense?

01:22:00.786 --> 01:22:04.360
So hopefully that was a blessing today.

01:22:10.530 --> 01:22:10.740
I just want more of Him.

01:22:13.349 --> 01:22:13.619
I just want to be with Him.

01:22:17.360 --> 01:22:19.413
I watch The Chosen, and I see Peter walking on the water, and he said, "Don't let me go, Jesus.

01:22:19.413 --> 01:22:20.569
Don't let me go.

01:22:20.569 --> 01:22:26.159
" And I sit there and I say, "Yeah, don't let me go, Jesus.

01:22:26.159 --> 01:22:40.091
I know You said You'd never leave me and You'll never forsake me, but I don't want You just walking.

01:22:56.380 --> 01:22:56.760
I want You holding me.

01:22:56.760 --> 01:22:58.297
I want it.

01:22:58.297 --> 01:23:01.880
I don't want to just walk with You.

01:23:01.880 --> 01:23:05.000
I want to sit in Your lap.

01:23:06.480 --> 01:23:20.740
" And that may sound really weird for a big, grown man like me to want to sit in Jesus' lap, but I just want to be that close to Him because, you know what?

01:23:21.760 --> 01:23:22.667
You can hear Him breathe.

01:23:22.667 --> 01:23:28.859
I want to experience the greatest manifestation of the glory that this world has ever seen before.

01:23:31.739 --> 01:23:41.200
And if I just get to be a part of it and it doesn't have anything to do with me, I'm okay with that.

01:23:51.510 --> 01:23:51.780
I just want to sit, I just want to be in that room.

01:23:51.780 --> 01:23:53.636
That's what I'm talking about.

01:24:04.180 --> 01:24:04.840
I want to see the paralyzed be lowered down from the roof and see Jesus touch them.

01:24:04.840 --> 01:24:11.600
I just want to be a part of it and see it.

01:24:20.937 --> 01:24:21.269
I want to see my Master work.

01:24:21.269 --> 01:24:25.460
But there's levels of saturation, and there's levels of the glory.

01:24:39.1000 --> 01:24:40.453
And the Lord told me, He said, "There's qualifications for it.

01:24:40.453 --> 01:24:43.679
" That was what I was really trying to get to.

01:24:43.679 --> 01:24:45.332
There's qualifications for those levels.

01:24:45.332 --> 01:24:46.810
There's qualifications for the levels.

01:24:46.810 --> 01:24:48.106
How much have you surrendered?

01:24:51.760 --> 01:24:52.120
So, I talked about a lot tonight.

01:25:01.200 --> 01:25:01.680
I don't even know how long I've been now.

01:25:20.399 --> 01:25:21.120
It's at an hour and eight, hour probably, hour and 10, hour and 15.

01:25:21.120 --> 01:25:23.792
So, did you get anything out of that?

01:25:23.792 --> 01:25:24.594
Did it encourage you at all?

01:25:24.594 --> 01:25:27.455
Did it help you with your walk?

01:25:37.712 --> 01:25:37.880
I pray it did.

01:25:38.551 --> 01:25:44.320
To walk, walking in the light of God.

01:25:55.940 --> 01:25:56.450
I'm excited to see what happens.

01:25:56.450 --> 01:25:58.023
Sister Billy's asleep.

01:26:08.560 --> 01:26:08.750
I'm just, you know, y'all.

01:26:09.130 --> 01:26:13.422
I'm tired of going to church and not expecting God to show up and show off.

01:26:13.422 --> 01:26:30.800
And if there's too much self reserved for self and He can't move because Brandon's in the way, man, let's just keep on the potter's wheel so we can get this thing going, because He showed me it was all attached to the glory.

01:26:30.800 --> 01:26:35.999
Walking in love, treating your brother right, doing all the things that are connected to the glory.

01:26:35.999 --> 01:26:44.579
It's all connected to the glory, the glorious church, dying to self, doing all these things.

01:26:55.600 --> 01:26:55.920
So, how many's here?

01:26:55.920 --> 01:26:56.293
3.

01:26:56.293 --> 01:26:56.667
5.

01:26:56.667 --> 01:26:57.040
Okay.

01:26:57.040 --> 01:26:59.679
Well, Father, we just thank You for Your glorious day You have for us as we get ready to start our next day.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
We thank You, Father, for Your body that was broken for us.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
And, Lord, I thank You that You're my friend.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.700
Lord, even though I walk through the valley of the shadow of death, I fear no evil, for You are with me.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
Thy rod and Thy staff, they comfort me.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
